description	"Greedo

Class Summary: 
Fast quick-throwing grenadier and pistoleer class.

Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (3)
- V-59 Concussion Grenade
- Frag Grenade (can only be quick thrown)

Attributes:
- Mind Trick Immunity
- Melee Damage Reduction
- Explosive Damage Reduction (Blast Armor)
- Quick Throw (alt ability 1)
- Heal (3)
- Dodge (1)
- Dash (2)

Greedo was a Rodians of planet Rodia. The Rodians are a species of green-skinned humanoids found throughout the galaxy. Greedo was a male Rodian bounty hunter who grew up on Tatooine in Mos Espa. During the Clone Wars, he was hired by the Trade Federation to kidnap Chi Eekway Papanoida and Che Amanwe Papanoida, the daughters of Chairman Papanoida, but was forced by the chairman to lead him and his son Ion to them. He was occasionally hired by crimelord Jabba the Hutt for various mercenary jobs, including the capture of Han Solo."